  "prompt": "Where can I get IIIT hyderabad question paper of 2016 for MTech of CS branch?",
  "response": "Obtaining the IIIT Hyderabad M.Tech. (CS) question paper from 2016 can be done through the following methods:\n\n1. **Official IIIT Hyderabad Website**:  \n   Visit the official IIIT Hyderabad website and check the \"Academics\" or \"Resources\" section. Many institutions upload previous years' question papers for student reference.\n\n2. **Department or Faculty**:  \n   Reach out to the Computer Science department or your professors at IIIT Hyderabad. They might have access to or can guide you to the question papers.\n\n3. **Library Resources**:  \n   The IIIT Hyderabad library might have archives of previous years' question papers. Visit the library or contact the librarian for assistance.\n\n4. **Student Communities or Seniors**:  \n   Connect with seniors or student communities at IIIT Hyderabad. Many students share question papers through WhatsApp groups, Google Drive, or other platforms.\n\n5. **Online Forums and Websites**:  \n   Websites like **Scribd**, **SlideShare**, or **GitHub** may have uploaded question papers. Use search terms like \"IIIT Hyderabad M.Tech CS 2016 question paper.\"\n\n6. **Alumni Network**:  \n   Reach out to IIIT Hyderabad alumni through LinkedIn or other professional networks. They might have saved question papers from their time at the institute.\n\nRemember to respect copyright and institutional policies when accessing or sharing question papers. Always verify the authenticity of the material you obtain.",
